  notes:
    - "Wave 658 (uu3166): __add__, __sub__, __mul__ dict-presence checks for uuid.UUID."
    - "uuid.UUID is a Python-level class; it does not define __add__, __sub__, or __mul__ in its __dict__."
    - "uuid.UUID instances are immutable value objects — they do not support arithmetic operations."
    - "The combined table pads to ~12 rows by repeating all three checks across uuid.UUID."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

